headline: The S&P 500 Will Get a Bit More Digital When the Index Makes Its Next Change Thursday
summary: With each change to the S&P 500, the index that dominates becomes a bit more like the digital world that dominates daily life. Come Thursday, Interactive Brokers Group will join the broad market measure, taking the place of Walgreens Boots Alliance.
